<p>Out-of-House Memberships are ideal for anyone who lives outside of Risley Hall and would like to have privileges that members of our community have!&nbsp;</p>

<p><u><strong>Privileges include:</strong></u></p>

<ul>
	<li>Card Access to Risley</li>
	<li>Use of the Risley Kitchens&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Use of the shops (sewing/leather, woodshop, jewelry, letterpress, film, editing, recording studio, digital media, ceramics, stained glass, dark room, art studio)</li>
	<li>Library and archive access</li>
	<li>Invitation to all Risley events&nbsp;</li>
	<li>Access to Dance Studio and Music Room</li>
	<li>Subscription to Risley ListServ&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<p><b><u>Out-of-House Membership Fee:</u></b>&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li>$50.00 per semester&nbsp;</li>
	<li>$90.00 per academic year&nbsp;</li>
</ul>

<p>Interested in becoming an Out-of-House member? Please fill out the 2017 Risley Hall Out-of-House <a href="https://orgsync.com/116633/forms/240043">Membership Application</a>&nbsp;today!</p>

